    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.192028>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 16. Photos of Sardinian centipedes. 15. Predation of Lithobius sbordonii Matic on Alpionisucus fragilis Budde-Lund (Crustacea, Isopoda, Trichoniscidae) in the cave of Su Molente near Codula Ilune (Nuoro province, without cadastre number) (photo by G. Dussoni, 17. III. 2007). 16. Plutonium zwierleini Cavanna in the cave “ Nurra ‘ e Pradu ” Sa / NU 3083 (Nuoro province) (photo by L. Sanna, 9. XI. 2008)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/192028/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

